	<div class="article-detail-bd">
			<div class="excerpt">
				“专利流氓”让不少大公司都吃尽苦头，Google 能解决这个顽疾吗？
			</div>
		<div class="detail">
				<!-- 普通文章 -->
				<p class="MsoNormal">
	没有任何产品、却搜罗各种专利用于起诉别人的公司，一般被称为“专利流氓”（<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Patent&nbsp;Troll</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">）。苹果、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">等巨头都吃过他们的苦头：苹果去年&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">2&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月输给&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Smartflash&nbsp;LLC&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">公司<a href="http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2015/02/25/company-without-a-product-wins-533m-verdict-vs-apple-says-its-no-patent-troll/" target="_blank">一场&nbsp;</a></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><a href="http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2015/02/25/company-without-a-product-wins-533m-verdict-vs-apple-says-its-no-patent-troll/" target="_blank">5.33&nbsp;</a></span><span style="font-family:宋体;"><a href="http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2015/02/25/company-without-a-product-wins-533m-verdict-vs-apple-says-its-no-patent-troll/" target="_blank">亿美元的专利官司</a></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">；</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">在卖掉摩托罗拉之前，也不停面临起诉，从&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">2011&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">到&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">2014&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年，</span><a href="http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/4/5375304/intellectual-ventures-goes-to-trial-against-google-and-motorola" target="_blank"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Intellectual&nbsp;Ventures&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">公司告了&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;"><a href="http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/4/5375304/intellectual-ventures-goes-to-trial-against-google-and-motorola" target="_blank">和摩托罗拉三次</a></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<a href="http://www.rpxcorp.com/" target="_blank"><span style="font-family:宋体;">根据反“专利流氓”公司&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">RPX&nbsp;</span></a><span style="font-family:宋体;"><a href="http://www.rpxcorp.com/" target="_blank">的说法</a></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，单是&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">2014&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">年全球因这类专利诉讼损失的诉讼费就高达&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">122&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">亿美元。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	一般来说，大公司之间的“专利战”往往能取得一定平衡，比如当年苹果起诉三星侵犯专利时，三星也能以类似的诉讼加以还击。相当一部分大公司之间的专利纠纷都会以相互授权专利的形式解决。可面对那种没有任何实体产品、没法告的公司，巨头们的“诉讼反击”就无能为力了。
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	为了从源头上扼杀“专利流氓”，<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google 宣布</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">推出试验性的专利交易平台“</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><a href="http://www.google.com/patents/licensing/" target="_blank">Patent&nbsp;Purchase&nbsp;Promotion</a></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">”</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">，让持有美国专利的个人直接向&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">兜售自己的专利。</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">专利问题法律顾问&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Allen&nbsp;Lo 在</span><span style="font-family:宋体;"><a href="http://googlepublicpolicy.blogspot.com/2015/04/announcing-patent-purchase-promotion.html" target="_blank">昨天发表的博客中</a>认为</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">：“这有望为专利持有人创造更好的体验，并消除‘专利流氓’引起的混乱局面。”</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	新<span style="font-family:宋体;">的&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Patent&nbsp;Purchase&nbsp;Promotion&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平台将在&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">5&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">8&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日到&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">22&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日之间开放，专利持有人可以在网上向&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">提交申请，并为自己的专利定个价，目前范围还仅限于在美国注册的专利。</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">称他们将在平台关闭之后查看每一份申请，遇到感兴趣的，会在&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">6&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">26&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日前通知申请人。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><a href="http://static.googleusercontent.com/media/www.google.com/zh-CN/us/patents/licensing/doc/patent-palooza-more-information.pdf" target="_blank">Google&nbsp;</a></span><span style="font-family:宋体;"><a href="http://static.googleusercontent.com/media/www.google.com/zh-CN/us/patents/licensing/doc/patent-palooza-more-information.pdf" target="_blank">发布的具体日程安排</a></span><span style="font-family:宋体;">显示，随后&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">会要求这些被选中的申请人在&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">7&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">8&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日前提交有关专利的更多详细信息。如果一切顺利，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">预计会在&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">7&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">月&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">22&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">日前掏钱买下中意的专利。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	Google&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体;">认为专利市场长期混乱的一个原因在于不少专利持有人将专利卖给“专利流氓”，因此他们希望用&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Patent&nbsp;Purchase&nbsp;Promotion&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平台将专利交易的过程公开，直接和专利持有人建立联系。不过这个项目现在还只是试验性的，结果如何尚难以定论。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<a href="（http://www.wired.com/2015/04/google-wants-buy-patent-keep-away-trolls/" target="_blank">《连线》杂志在报道中认为</a><span style="font-family:宋体;">，这个专利交易平台还能为&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">提供更多有价值的信息，比如当前市面上还有哪些专利、它们价值几何等等。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	同时，<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Patent&nbsp;Purchase&nbsp;Promotion&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平台还可能成为&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">的专利防御系统。所谓专利防御系统，就是通过收购专利授权给客户，以免其陷入专利诉讼的泥淖中，类似的公司有&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';"><a href="http://www.rpxcorp.com/" target="_blank">RPX</a>&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">等等。</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	不过说起来，<span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Intellectual&nbsp;Ventures&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">最早也是一个专利防御系统，甚至&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">还给它投过最初的启动资金，而今却成了<a href="http://www.theverge.com/2014/2/4/5375304/intellectual-ventures-goes-to-trial-against-google-and-motorola" target="_blank">全球最大、最著名的“专利流氓”</a>。如果&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Patent&nbsp;Purchase&nbsp;Promotion&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">平台试验成功并逐渐成型，也可能成为&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Google&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">对付其它科技巨头的“弹药库”。</span><span style="font-family:宋体;">此前 Google 在专利战方面一直扮演防御角色，没有主动攻击竞争对手的习惯，但未来如果形势发生变化，不知道还会不会保持“不作恶”？</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	<span style="font-family:宋体;"><br />
</span> 
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">
	图片来源：<span style="color:#3D3C40;font-family:Lato, appleLogo, sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;"><a href="http://www.hellorf.com/" target="_blank">站酷海洛创意</a></span> 
</p>
